    <!-- DEPLOYMENT TEXT -->
    <string name="about_text">Firsthand is a project from the Huffington post to hear your stories about what is happening where you live.\n\n
Every month, with your input, we will focus on a particular challenge and invite you to show us through photos, a few sentences, or video how the issue affects you.\n\n
Only by gathering all of our stories together can we reflect the true state of our communities.\n\n
Ushahidi is a non-profit tech company that specializes in developing free and open source software for information collection, visualization, and interactive mapping.</string>

